# Domain Knowledge — Manual Review Required

This folder contains project-specific knowledge that helps Phoenix generate
better automation. **You must manually review and update these files** with
information about YOUR application.

## Why This Matters

Phoenix uses AI to generate tests. The AI understands general web patterns
(forms, buttons, navigation), but it cannot know the specific quirks of YOUR
application without being told.

For example:
- Does your app use custom dropdown components? (Document in ui_patterns.md)
- Are there non-standard URL patterns? (Document in navigation.md)
- Do fields have special validation rules? (Document in data_rules.md)

The more context you provide here, the better Phoenix's generated tests will be.

## What to Document

See the template files (ui_patterns.md, navigation.md, data_rules.md) for
examples of useful information to capture.

## ⚠ Manual Review Required

These files are NOT auto-generated. You must fill them in manually as you
learn about your application's behaviour.
